reviewText: Just love these guys and their tips.
I enjoyed this show.  It was good fun and learned some things too.
Jai Rodriguez was worth every penny and Kyan extra pleasant bonus. Jai is so beyond fine it was worth every penny I spent
Amusingly given, great tips for half a dozen breeders who really needed the help... It just goes to prove queer guys have a lot to offer... : )
A Queer Eye DVD collection would not be complete with this...although it doesn't contain as many humorous outtakes as the others, until complete season DVDs become available, I'll take it!
